model.name: Trompe L’Oeil Shirt
model.disambiguatingDescription: This Trompe L’Oeil Shirt morphs two casual classics into a single eye-catching piece. Tailored in a slightly loose fit from coating cotton, it reproduces denim jacket details on the front to create a trompe l’oeil effect. Its distorted metallic tone-on-tone buttons are a seasonal signature.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• 100% Cotton
  • White
  • Slightly Loose Fit
  • Model wears a FR M size
  • Model measurements : chest 32’’ / 82 cm, height 6’’ / 183 cm.
  • Made in Italy
